{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "失樂園", "storyInfo": "數日後，杜林人開始向地上轉移，而斯第奇也在為讓際崖城在毀滅前回歸完美而工作著，意外地，他讀到了自己老師留下的信。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g4_durinsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i10", "xScale": 0.9, "yScale": 0.9, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 20.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數日後"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天，斯第奇也在廣場上努力著。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打扮城市的遺容與前往地面一樣，都是需要全城居民來監督的行動。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而穹頂作為一座城市的臉面，自然是重中之重。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，就變成了需要在廣場上當著所有人的面進行設計工作。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶奇大師美其名曰：節省時間。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡的臭老頭，一定只是單純覺得這樣比較有趣。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇看著耶奇在下面洋洋得意的樣子，氣得牙癢癢。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，就連他自己都沒有想到，他其實適應得並不慢。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當他不得不面對路過的人的詢問，當他即使不想聽也聽到了其他人的意見，當他甚至因為堅持自己的意見而和人大吵一架時——"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切並沒有如想像中那樣給他帶來壓力。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如對現在在下方壞笑的耶奇老頭那樣，他雖然恨得牙癢癢，但他知道了別人是怎麼想的。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像別人也知道了他是怎麼想的一樣。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這小子，結果這幾天沒少跟人吵架。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別人提一點意見都要和人爭個半天。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，給出的東西倒確實讓人沒話說。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，芬奇啊，雖然不知道你這老小子現在在幹什麼，不過你應該可以放心了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，對了對了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹什麼，我忙著呢！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，在先前檢查穹頂的時候，有人在穹頂的尖端發現了一封信。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，而且，是給你的信。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說......？！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#4$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我是芬奇·畫布，際崖城最偉大的建築設計師。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這封信被我放在了穹頂之尖。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "打開它的應該是下一任負責改造這個穹頂的人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我希望那會是我最親愛的徒弟。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這是我留給他的信。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但如果那個人不是他，那麼，請你不要交給他。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為這說明他失敗了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g9_collapsedtunnel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡奇，對不起。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我也像你一樣......", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個人的性格都不一樣，你的想法我也能夠理解。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只能說，我如果早一點察覺到的話，事情可能會不太一樣吧。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在留下來也沒關係的。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#5$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，總覺得對你做了不好的事情啊，卡奇老弟。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會啊，極境哥，我很感謝你當時給我的建議。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然一開始確實是為了刺激斯第奇做出的決定，但是，我也是真心想要找到芬奇大師的蹤跡的。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別的不說，告訴他斯第奇現在的狀況，他老人家一定也會開心吧。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你啊，真是讓人不知道說什麼好。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，那位芬奇大師既然還是很關心弟子的，我猜測，他也有可能前往地上尋找解決礦石病的方法。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我回去之後，也會想辦法找一找他的蹤跡。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，有一天他找到了我們羅德島也說不定呢。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，那太好了！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我說這些的意思，對吧？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我們還會再見面的。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還想著重建際崖城的時候能夠出一份力呢。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，我一定要和斯第奇一起做一些了不起的設計。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_inspiration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如一座我的雕像？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這——恐怕還是不行。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_571_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "首先，老師要為自己的離開道歉。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但如果我不這麼做，以你的性格，你將永遠無法獨立。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "好吧，主要是我如果留在你身邊，也沒法真的把你放著不管。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你很有天賦，斯第奇·畫布。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "礦石病讓你的生命變得短暫，但是同時，它也讓你對生命的思考變得更加深刻。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這讓你的風格有了進一步的蛻變。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這些，我都看在眼裡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_caveentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_axehitscrape"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_axehitscrape"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都給我打起精神來，今天我們的任務是要把這一片的洞穴結構全給它打通！", "name": "興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到了嗎，尤吉！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，哥哥！", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼啊，尤塔，你也不用這麼早就起來開工吧。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼呢，依娜姆。", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是嘉維爾給我們下達的任務。", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她救了我的命，我可是恨不得現在立刻就挖穿地底去見見她，看她現在過得好不好。", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你死她都不會死的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，那當然！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我打算明天就啟程去面見帕夏，談一談有關王酋的事情。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，明天開始，你們都歸祖瑪瑪管，明白了嗎？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不要我跟你一起去？", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是說，帕夏都不是什麼好東西嗎？", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就你，你跟我去只會更加被吃得骨頭都不剩。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我這些年信使也不是白當的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，祖瑪瑪，這邊就交給你了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暴躁鐵皮的特製裝備，“穿山斧MKIII”也已經裝好了。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我們的效率會翻個三倍左右。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡交給我一個人都可以。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#2"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有的時候，我會覺得你比嘉維爾可能還要恐怖一點。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但同時，這也讓你的性格變得愈發偏激。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在對自己風格愈發堅持的同時，你變得越來越不喜歡和他人交流。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這讓我感到擔憂。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，阿芙朵嘉，你去了地面之後，打算怎麼辦啊？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼怎麼辦？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該不會以為我那麼說了以後，就真的打算在地面安穩生活了吧？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#4$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到際崖城重建時，我會跟著回來的。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......其實是我回想起來，之前有一次和依娜姆說好了。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果未來我要前往地上的話，會和她做生意，她給我介紹了一個叫做羅德島的地方。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我不是對地上不瞭解嘛，我當時就說你會代替我和她打交道，然後我會從中學習。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把我賣了？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起！但是我真的很想試試在地面上做生意的感覺，幫幫我，阿芙朵嘉！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿芙朵嘉", "delay": 0.1, "content": "克，羅，綺，磚，石！"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿芙朵嘉", "content": "我不是說過了，讓你不要喝酒的嗎！"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的很對不起！！！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當曲高和寡不是一個結果時，它往往會成為一種錯覺，斯第奇。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它告訴你不被理解不是你的問題，它告訴你你的作品不被認可是他人的錯。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但有的時候事實並非如此。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你當然可以堅持自己的思考。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是，若你的思考竟然真的精妙到只有你自己能理解，那你豈不是更應該將你精妙的思考分享給他人？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g4_durinsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#8$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "ypos": 30.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，這根柱子放這裡就行了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到連廣場都打算修繕一遍，杜林人做事還真是徹底啊。", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "fadetime": 0.3, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有意識到，你正在創造歷史？", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在地下生活了漫長的時間，從未和地上的人有過大規模交流的杜林人。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你的決定和影響之下，居然一次性地以一座城的人口這樣的規模遷往了地上。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿卡胡拉竟是這片大地上第一個與杜林城邦和杜林人開展密切交流的地區。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而當未來的人回頭看來時，他們恐怕怎麼也想不到，這竟然只是你嘉維爾一拍腦袋提出的方法。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼一說，好像確實是這麼一回事。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這樣也沒什麼不好吧？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，當然沒有什麼不好。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要說的正是——歷史總是這樣的，嘉維爾。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像，杜林能夠在地下站穩腳跟，或許也只是一個意外。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這似乎在說明，歷史就和被你輕而易舉破壞的阿卡胡拉傳統一樣，或許並沒有那麼值得敬畏。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒是不好說，懂歷史的傢伙我覺得都挺厲害的。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如凱爾希醫生就很懂。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希？嗯......實際上從我和她為數不多的交流來看，她或許是這片大地上對於歷史最輕蔑的人。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，她的輕蔑或許更像是一種基於瞭解的無可奈何。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，這是另一個話題。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖瑪瑪和我說過，你也對這個決定猶豫過，但你堅持了下來，而你未來也打算堅持下去，對吧？", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，因為祖瑪瑪她們說，她們也會幫我的。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼一說，老爺子，你也會一直跟我們在一起吧？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，居然連我這個老頭子都不放過，真是有你的，嘉維爾。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很顯然，我現在非常滿意跟祖瑪瑪一起研究機械的生活。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能明白嗎，活得太久就會很難尋找目標的感覺。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不明白。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不明白就對了，我就是喜歡你這一點，嘉維爾。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往前走吧，我也很好奇，你到底能夠走到哪一步。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，老爺子你為什麼不跟著祖瑪瑪？來我這邊說這些。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "大祭司", "content": "那當然是因為——"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "大祭司", "content": "我被她趕出來了！"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是說杜林們造的機器沒有大醜可愛，她就生氣了。", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，她居然這麼護著她的新朋友，我也要生氣了！", "name": "大祭司"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_074"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_074", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "有的事情不親身體驗永遠無法理解。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "所以我給你留下了一個難題。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在沒有成為下一任的設計代表之前，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在沒有說服所有際崖城的人相信你的作品有深刻意義之前。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會離開你的身邊，並且不允許你來找我。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們是建築設計師，我們的工作是提供讓大部分人滿意的設計。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你將會發現，你遇到的最大難題，不是設計上的缺陷，也不是施工上的困難，竟然只是簡單的——說服他人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_caveentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_elevator", "volume": 0.3, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇哦，特米米，你感覺到了嗎？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是震動。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都已經乘坐升降梯上來了，居然還能夠感覺得到。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這動靜可真是不小。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，際崖城的居民已經全部來到地面了，一個人都沒有少哦！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，大家都做得很好。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#2$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事吧，跟你說了不要逞強，結果你也非要留到最後一個。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城市崩塌到底有什麼靈感可以吸取的。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟你說了你也不明白。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#6$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是一座城市的最後一刻，真是......令人感慨。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#11$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......老師，雖然這對我來說確實很難，但我會盡可能地試一試的。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這小子，在夢裡自言自語什麼呢。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他......看起來很累的樣子。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也難怪，這段時間，倒真是辛苦他了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，不僅真的讓他設計了出來，施工時他還天天跑現場，而且堅持最後一個走。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這傢伙，之前那個樣子還真看不出他這麼負責。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我也對斯第奇有些刮目相看了！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，走吧。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是最後了，大家還在等著我們呢。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungle_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘉維爾怎麼還沒出來，該不會出事了吧？！", "name": "尤吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別咒她！", "name": "尤塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來了。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉怎麼還不來，我還急著要去瀑布玩呢。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以先去。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可不行，這個叫怎麼說的來著，對了，歷史性的一幕！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦洞前，杜林與提亞卡烏們將洞口團團圍住。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都在等待著最後幾個乘坐升降梯上來的人。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$marketplace_intro", "key": "$marketplace_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i12", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 0.9, "yScaleTo": 0.9, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶著一如既往的笑容，嘉維爾抱著斯第奇走了出來。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她舉起自己的右手，向那些面露笑容的人們打了一聲招呼。"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天是個好日子，各位，就讓我們去湖裡玩個痛快吧！", "name": "嘉維爾"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音未落，人群中就爆發出了熱烈的歡呼聲。"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的阿卡胡拉，比往常要熱鬧一些。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而未來，恐怕會更加熱鬧。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}